	(text "Probe is baised on work done by the Marco Carminati and Paolo Luzzatto-Fegiz. \nConduino CC-BY-SA 4.0 (https://github.com/feslab/conduino). As modified \nby the OpenCPD team CC-BY-SA 4.0 (Conduino-V01.pdf).\n\nPCB design development baised on the DFRobot Gravity EC Sensor DFR0300"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
