	)
	(text "The range is determined by feedback resistor R10. R12 will have very little effect.\n\nIf you want it to be less sensitive (higher conductivity) then you would reduce R10 proportionally. \n\nhttps://electronics.stackexchange.com/questions/695895/modifying-a-tds-module-for-higher-electrical-conductivity-measurements"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
